{"tid":173623,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"多女仔主動想識我，求解","createTime":"2017-03-26T09:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T14:29:17.000Z","uid":82725,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b06b4fa558c0e05ea1aa9d984507b0cd3de12b9b","tid":173623,"uid":82725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"身為一個女仔<br />\n我由細到大朋友都唔多，<br />\n係正正常常個啲。<br />\n<br />\n由細到大都有好多女仔痴埋我身邊<br />\n個時諗唔係好明，單純覺得女性緣特別好<br />\n係特別好中意痴住我玩（No FF)<br />\n種要係個個都好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直到出埋社會做嘢<br />\n都不停有女仔朋友keep 住想contact 我<br />\n我就覺得唔係我諗多左<br />\n<br />\n反而以前男性朋友一個都無，覺得好難同男仔相處<br />\n我第一個交心嘅男仔仲要係中五個年嘅留堂班<br />\n佢好唔開心，之後<br />\n我主動Hi佢先識到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然好多人鍾意痴住我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我自己中意獨處，我中意自己一個，中意自己同自己玩，行街睇戲食飯旅行（一個月）一個人冇難度，完全唔明點解而家啲人話要挑戰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一放假留返啲時間俾自己，玩消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過自己睇急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，覺得無乜嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心唔明點解D女仔咁鍾意痴住我玩，WhatsApp我已經係日覆，佢哋係秒覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：覺得交際應酬好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實毒l一個更開心，其實有無巴絲都係咁？"},{"pid":"dd8b2d1c4597c8f48ed783c9668dc0699294b799","tid":173623,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:56:47.000Z","msg":"5p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee27207bee1703e46da6ff805e902e2b0d897e62","tid":173623,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"好受歡迎啊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4820b6aaa423f773fa9a82d41474270fb0a797fb",